    <h1>Citation Audit</h1>
    <p class="description">A systematic review of every online mention of your business NAP — used to find duplicates, wrong addresses, and missing directories that quietly suppress <strong>local pack rankings</strong>.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
          <span class="meta-author-role">Marketing Head · theStacc</span>
        </div>
      </div>
