            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>A manual audit of 50 directories takes 2 to 4 hours. Automated tools like BrightLocal, Whitespark, or Moz Local scan the same directories in under 10 minutes and return a formatted report.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">What do I do after finding citation errors?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Prioritize by directory importance. Fix Google Business Profile, Bing Places, and Yelp first, then push corrections through the four data aggregators (Data Axle, Neustar, Foursquare, Factual), then work down individual directories.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Do citation audits still matter in 2026?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
