          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Can I audit citations for free?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes — most audit tools offer a free scan of the top 30 directories. Full audits with aggregator status and 80+ directory coverage are paid, but the free scan is enough to identify duplicate GBP listings and major inconsistencies.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

